extendedInfo.description: You love Damn You Auto Correct on the web... now enjoy it on the go with hundreds of funny screenshots of auto correct fails on this new app for your Android phone.This is the official app of DYAC, as seen on Gizmodo, Comedy Central, HuffPo, CNN, ABC, and hundreds of news sites worldwide. This easy to use app will let you swipe your way through thousands of funny text messages from the DYAC website. New autocorrect fails will be frequently added so the laughs will keep coming. SUBMIT IMAGES EASILY: Did you witness a funny auto correct moment? Take a screen shot and easily submit it to us with the built-in form.

reviews.title: Good and funny
reviews.comment: Positives- funny and mood enlightening. Negatives- you have to scroll to find where you left off and you can\'t save messages you think are the best. Suggestions- make it save where you left off, make it to where you can post messages to it without going to the website, and categorize it so you can choose what kind of messages you want to read instead of them going on and on. Rating 3 but I\'ll give 5 if you do as i suggested. Thanks :)
reviews.author: Caitlyn Givens
